265
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:52,750
Government silver? Seal?

266
00:21:52,750 --> 00:21:57,750
Is this the seal to instruct the delivery of the government silver during the third year of Taiyan?

267
00:21:57,750 --> 00:22:02,650
