316
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:17,520
Thank you, Sister. I'm leaving.

317
00:26:30,140 --> 00:26:34,190
Grandmother was kind to let her learn the accounts. In the end,

318
00:26:34,190 --> 00:26:38,250
