319
00:26:38,250 --> 00:26:40,040
Older Sister.

320
00:26:43,370 --> 00:26:47,920
The third year of Taiyan was a long time ago. We must plan to obtain the accounts of that year.

321
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:53,200
