401
00:32:30,610 --> 00:32:32,820
I indeed have another thing.

402
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:38,070
Is your father Jun Yingwen?

403
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:42,000
Do you know my father?

404
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:43,800
I have heard of him.

405
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:46,100
